headline: 3 Reasons We Love McKesson (MCK)
summary: McKesson currently trades at $712.18 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 332% since June 2020, blowing past the S&P 500’s 83.5% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 18%.
